         <abstract id="aspace_0a1ea70fc3437ca55e2da4548a123569">The collection consists of research notes and publicity materials for the book,<title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>The Art and Architecture of Paul Rudolph</part>
            </title>, by Anthony John Monk. The collection also includes photographs and slides of several Rudolph buildings, as well as presentation boards for the Paisley Civic Center project in Scotland by the architectural firm Hutchinson Locke and Monk.</abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_5189e1fc28dc51ad6f3a05e5e6412cbd">
            <language>The papers are in English and Japanese.</language>
         </langmaterial>
