            <scopecontent id="aspace_ddad33173e11b2ca902f74f7733e0ed6">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This event was held at the American Embassy in London commemorating the launch of the book<title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>The Art and Architecture of Paul Rudolph</part>
                  </title>, by Tony Monk. Introduction by American Ambassador Philip Lader; lecture by Tony Monk; and debate between Lord Norman Foster, Charles Jenks, Tony Monk, and Martin Pawley. Produced by the University of Luton.</p>
            </scopecontent>
